_sText:
Surf map made by Cheetah 

On the Top you can press 3 Buttons to break the glass.
There are some secrets .. :)

In the "Admin room" there are some buttons, which sets friendlyfire on/off, airaccelerate 100/1000/10, gravity 200/800/1000.

You have to press a button on the hightes platform. Then you can use the keypad to open the Admin room door.
